data.description: BEAUTIFUL 2 Bed 2 Bath, POOL home on .39 Acres with oak trees. Enter the arched entryway to the LIVING/DINING ROOM combo. Kitchen features WOOD CABINETS, JETTA STONE COUNTERTOPS, BREAKFAST BAR, TILE BACKSPLASH, and SS APPLIANCES. Separate BREAKFAST NOOK off kitchen. FAMILY ROOM with FIREPLACE, Skylight, and Laminate Floors. INSIDE Utility ROOM. The ENCLOSED PATIO with insulated windows and french doors leads to the gorgeous pool. Pool inc: Salt Water Sports Pool, Pavers, In-Floor Cleaning System, Diamond Brite Finish w/2 Seats & Vaulted Screen Enclosure. This PRIVATE backyard with no rear neighbors, includes a PRIVATE WELL FOR IRRIGATION, UTILITY SHED, DOG RUN and PAVED GAZEBO. BRING YOUR BOAT OR RV!, NO HOA, and FLOOD ZONE X. ROOF 2022, A/C 2013, WATER HEATER 2017. Some newer windows.
